 Pointers for Writing a Genius (Even If You Aren’t One)</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">September 12, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/jackanderson/">Jack Anderson</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/contrary-to-popular-belief-people-do-just-vanish/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/09/missing-vanished-feat-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/contrary-to-popular-belief-people-do-just-vanish/">Contrary to Popular Belief, <br>People <em>Do</em> Just Vanish</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">September 12, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/mariamalone/">Maria Malone</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/my-first-thriller-meg-gardiner/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/09/Meg-Gardiner-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/my-first-thriller-meg-gardiner/">My First Thriller: Meg Gardiner</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">September 11, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/rickpullen/">Rick Pullen</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
